---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="SIGNAL - State Runtime" description="Internal diagnostic output">
  <div class="signal-page">
    <div class="signal-terminal mono">
      <pre class="signal-output">
STATE RUNTIME - DIAGNOSTIC SIGNAL
══════════════════════════════════

&gt; running test suite: @stateruntime/behave

  ✓ machine() creates valid state machine
  ✓ transition validates target state exists
  ✓ guard predicates prevent invalid transitions
  ✓ actions execute on transition
  ✓ nested states resolve correctly
  ✓ parallel regions maintain independence
  ✓ history states restore previous configuration
  ✓ serialization round-trips without data loss

  8 passed · 0 failed · 0 skipped
  elapsed: 12ms

&gt; running test suite: @stateruntime/fault

  ✓ ok() wraps value correctly
  ✓ err() wraps error correctly
  ✓ map() transforms ok values
  ✓ mapErr() transforms error values
  ✓ andThen() chains results
  ✓ unwrapOr() provides fallback
  ✓ match() exhaustively handles variants

  7 passed · 0 failed · 0 skipped
  elapsed: 8ms

══════════════════════════════════
ALL SYSTEMS NOMINAL
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .signal-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 48px;
    background: var(--black);
  }
  .signal-terminal {
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .signal-output {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--signal);
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }
</style>
